function Start()
	idIvaanjavClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(id_Ivaanjav, true)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idIvaanjavClone) then
		
		Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(conv_Ivaanjav_02, idSelf, idIvaanjavClone)
		-- possible to follow the player here?
		Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(idIvaanjavClone, conv_Ivaanjav_02)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idIvaanjavClone, 0.5)
		
	end
end
